Text:
No matter where you live, everyone wants to be able to get a job and keep a job.

No matter who you love, everyone wants to be able to buy a home and keep a home.

@JoeBiden and I understand that and together we’ll create an America where opportunity is within reach for everyone.

Once this pandemic is over, we can’t go back to the way things were. We need to #BuildBackBetter. 

@JoeBiden has a plan to do that. 

He’ll revitalize American manufacturing and create millions of good-paying jobs, ensuring the future is made in America—by all of America.
